00:19:23.245 --> 00:19:24.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nak bercium pun sukar.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:19:25.497 --> 00:19:26.957 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tak, bercium okey.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:19:29.293 --> 00:19:31.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shin, awak cium siapa? Nobu?</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:19:31.962 --> 00:19:35.174 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Adakah Nobu sukakan lelaki?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Betulkah begitu?</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:19:35.757 --> 00:19:38.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tidak, tapi saya fikir Shin suka lelaki.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:19:38.844 --> 00:19:40.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Saya suka perempuan.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:19:40.512 --> 00:19:42.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hei, Shin.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:19:42.389 --> 00:19:45.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Awak nak terus tinggal di rumah Nobu?</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:19:45.392 --> 00:19:49.229 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Kebelakangan ini,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>saya cuma pergi ke rumahnya sekali-sekala.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:19:49.313 --> 00:19:50.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Saya tak nak ganggu dia.</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:19:51.899 --> 00:19:53.442 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jadi, awak balik rumah?</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:19:53.525 --> 00:19:55.819 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Tidak.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Habis awak tinggal di mana?</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:19:55.903 --> 00:19:57.321 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Di rumah wanita.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:19:57.404 --> 00:19:58.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apa?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:19:58.906 --> 00:20:00.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Satu demi satu.</c.bg_transparent>

329
00:20:02.451 --> 00:20:07.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Saya masih 15 tahun dan berpakaian begini.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Saya tak dapat cari kerja yang bagus.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:20:07.331 --> 00:20:10.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tapi saya tahu saya</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>takkan ada masalah jika hidup begini.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:20:12.753 --> 00:20:14.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dunia ini mudah, bukan?</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:20:17.049 --> 00:20:20.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shin, awak memang tak guna.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:20:21.011 --> 00:20:21.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tak guna?</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:20:22.596 --> 00:20:26.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>- Nanti ada wanita bunuh awak.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>- Shin, saya sangat sedih.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:20:27.517 --> 00:20:28.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Nana.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:20:32.856 --> 00:20:35.234 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Shoji, awak lari ke mana?</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:20:35.317 --> 00:20:37.736 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Awak ada rancangan selepas ini?</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:20:37.819 --> 00:20:42.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tak, saya cuti empat hari mulai esok,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>jadi saya akan tunggu awak.</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:20:43.492 --> 00:20:44.701 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tak perlu tunggu.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:20:44.785 --> 00:20:45.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apa?</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:20:48.872 --> 00:20:52.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Boleh saya datang ke rumah nanti?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Kita perlu berbincang.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:20:55.003 --> 00:20:59.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Pada malam itu,</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>jika awak tak bersama saya,</i></c.bg_transparent>

343
00:20:59.758 --> 00:21:03.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>tentu saya akan terjun</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>ke dalam Sungai Tamagawa.</i></c.bg_transparent>

344
00:21:05.514 --> 00:21:08.141 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Saya benar-benar fikir begitu.</i></c.bg_transparent>

345
00:22:15.625 --> 00:22:17.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Terjemahan sari kata oleh Majdi Omar</c.bg_transparent>

